      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-sm-6 sm-card" id="card2">
    <div id="inner2">

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row" id="third-block">
  <div class="col-sm-6 sm-card" id="card3">
    <div id="inner3">

    </div>
    <%#= link_to "ADD A QUESTION" %>
  </div>
  <div class="col-sm-6 sm-card" id="card4">
    <div id="inner4">
      <h1>- Processing -</h1>
      <p>
        Behind the scenes, Speechable works to <br>
        tell you if you hit your marks. 
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
